duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide emergency care and treatment to patients in the ED (Emergency Department) setting.
Assess patient conditions, prioritize care, and collaborate with healthcare team for patient stabilization.
Adhere to healthcare compliance standards and regulations for patient care and documentation.
Manage and implement care plans for patients based on assessment and diagnosis.
Effectively communicate and collaborate with healthcare team members to ensure coordinated patient care.
Participate in critical care scenarios and respond to emergency situations in a timely and effective manner.
